{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_05_02",
  "title": "miho",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "…………はぁ",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（まだ、葉さんの墓参りのことで悩んでるみたいだ）",
      "startTime": 2.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（もうすぐクリスマスライブのリハが始まるんだけど）\n（この調子で、大丈夫かな……）",
      "startTime": 9.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 11.9249436139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方が考えていることは、大体分かりますけど",
      "startTime": 11.9249436139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 15.5916102806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "昔、ここのイベントに出たことがありまして\nこの場所に来るのは、それ以来だなと思っただけです",
      "startTime": 18.8582767088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざご心配いただかずとも\n昔のことで、ステージに影響は出しませんよ",
      "startTime": 25.2249433755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "し、失礼しました",
      "startTime": 28.3249436139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.3249436139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、俺も昔、三枝さんの知り合いの手伝いで\nこの会場でバイトしたことがありますよ",
      "startTime": 34.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "当時はまだ高校に通ってたので、学校が終わってから\n現場に直行で、雑用をしたり、荷物を運ばされた記憶が",
      "startTime": 41.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 45.9096351981
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "それはご愁傷様でした",
      "startTime": 45.9096351981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "それと……私が気乗りしないのは\n単純に、このイベント会場があまり好きではないんです",
      "startTime": 52.6096362312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 56.0429685314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "昔、ちょっとしたトラブルがあったもので",
      "startTime": 56.0429685314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……トラブル？",
      "startTime": 59.5763018648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 62.0116316636
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 62.0116316636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、おかしいな……",
      "startTime": 63.0116321564,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6.665114600004074,
          "startTime": 63.018297271
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1976.7316023000062,
          "startTime": 64.9883637587
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんです？",
      "startTime": 66.2127217968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 67.8460558931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ここに置いたはずのクリアファイルがないんですよ\nどこにやったかな",
      "startTime": 71.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "当日のタイムスケジュール表や、関係者席のチケットが\n入っているので、なくしたとなると面倒なことに……",
      "startTime": 76.3333310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 80.4163670023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "………………はぁ\nまた、この会場でこういうことになるのね",
      "startTime": 82.2830316503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……『また』？",
      "startTime": 85.4497003357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 86.8578409552
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、この辺りにバンプロの方がいましたから\n間違って持って行ったのかもしれません",
      "startTime": 90.6245056032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "今なら、まだこのフロアにいるでしょうから……\n追いかけて、話を聞いてきて下さい",
      "startTime": 95.9578389365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました！",
      "startTime": 98.4578409552,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1613.7641667999958,
          "startTime": 100.071605122
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8982708135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんの言った通りでした\nバンプロさんが、自分達のものと間違えたそうで",
      "startTime": 104.9666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "クリアファイルなんて、似たり寄ったりですからね",
      "startTime": 108.4488615553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 111.6155282219
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "合同ライブですし、リハ中はみんなバタバタしてますし\nたまに荷物の取り違えがあるんですよ",
      "startTime": 115.7821826974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "経験豊富なmihoさんがいてくれて助かりましたよ\nま、トラブルの経験値はあまり積みたくないですけどね",
      "startTime": 121.9999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 126.4421991745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "……昔、ここのイベントに出た時に\nさっきのように荷物を取り違えられたんです",
      "startTime": 131.3755198079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 134.2755325078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "あの時も本番直前で、あちこちの事務所の人が\n出入りしていましたから",
      "startTime": 137.6421864746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんに付けてもらう小物やヘッドセットが\n入っていたバッグを、知らない人に持って行かれて",
      "startTime": 142.1070291439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 145.2755325078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "慌てて追いかけたんですけど、見失ってしまって……\n危うく、マイクなしでステージに立つところでした",
      "startTime": 149.2088531413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "それは災難でしたねぇ",
      "startTime": 152.5421991745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 155.4745660423
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_02-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "今にして思えば、妙なスタッフさんでしたね\n後ろ姿しか見ていませんが、なぜか学ランだったんです",
      "startTime": 159.6412205177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
